dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents recreation for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Outagamie_Recreation_2017.gdb. [This is a polygon shapefile identifying the location of all parks, trails, fishing areas, wildlife areas that are owned or operated by Outagamie County. The attributes contain the names of the specific areas and the 'major' municipality it is located in, as well as area and perimeter.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/ .This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
